27 y117e ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">teach? Acts 15: 1. Note 1. </div><div class="t m127 x34 h27 y133a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m977 x59 h27 y133a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What was the attitude of Paul and Barnabas in </div><div class="t m16c x74 h27 y1ce3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reference to what was taught? What did the brethren </div><div class="t m104a x74 h27 y1054 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">finally decide to do? Verse 2. Note 2. </div><div class="t m2b6 x34 h27 y1100 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m41f x59 h27 y1100 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Through what region did they pass on their way </div><div class="t m8cc x74 h27 y1e18 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to Jerusalem? What did they declare? What was the </div><div class="t m218 x74 h27 y1ddf ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">effect of their message on the believers? Verse 3. </div><div class="t ma2 x34 h27 y110f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m102 x59 h27 yead ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On meeting the church at Jerusalem, what did the </div><div class="t mae8 x73 h27 y20a8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">apostles do? Verse 4. </div><div class="t m1cd x34 h27 y1422 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m95 x59 h27 y1422 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who offered objections? What did they teach? </div><div class="t m13a x74 h27 y11b6 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 5. Note 3. </div><div class="t m1d0 x34 h27 y1193 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m87a x59 h27 y1193 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In view of the contention, what did the apostles and </div><div class="t m130d x74 h27 y1fda ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the elders do? Verse 6. Note 4. </div><div class="t m1d2 x34 h27 y1eb3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m19a x59 h27 y1374 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What spirit characterized the meeting in the be-</div><div class="t mb96 x74 h27 y1123 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ginning? Who finally spoke? To what did he refer? </div><div class="t m220 x74 h27 yd49 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verse 7. </div><div class="t m1b7c x6c h2e yd49 ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">e </div><div class="t m1d5 x34 h27 y1151 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m6b9 x59 h27 y1151 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What gift had been bestowed upon the believing </div><div class="t m14d x73 h27 y1152 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">gentiles? Verse 8. Note 5. </div><div class="t m127 x34 h27 y1ec3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t me28 x59 h27 y1ec2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How are all regarded by the Lord? How is the </div><div class="t m895 x73 h27 ybe6 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heart purified? Verse 9. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
